title: Ane-Koi
description:
0-5. Ane Koi (Sis Love)
[spoiler]
Akimasa is now a high-school student lives with his older sister who he obviously has feelings for "Mao-neechan". Aki's sister, for her part was pretty popular and well loved and responsible in school and is now a successful office lady, on the surface. But in reality she is much more troubled over Aki than what he will ever be over her. Can something possibly develop between the two of them?
...Meanwhile Aki's other sister, otaku Rio, and their adopted cousin, delinquent Asami, also suddenly realize that they want to be much closer to Aki than they are now. [/spoiler]
6-7. Suki Kirai Daisuki (Love, Hate, I Love You)
8. Kaichou no Uso to Honto (The Truth and Lies of the Student Council President)
9. Ane Sailor (Sailor Suit Sister)
10. Heya to Koinu to Masaki-san (The Room and the Puppy and Masaki-san)
